$DATA ../NMsimData_xgxr004_subprobs.csv IGN=@
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 TRANS4 $PK KA=THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) V2=THETA(2)*EXP(ETA(2)) CL=THETA(3)*EXP(ETA(3)) V3=THETA(4)*EXP(ETA(4)) Q=THETA(5)*EXP(ETA(5))
